{"tid":2209916,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"繁體字係咪應該要叫返做正體字？","createTime":"2020-09-20T04:20:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T14:48:29.000Z","uid":365620,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"44b9e6bd0e02d2aaf365841eed34bb788eb8046a","tid":2209916,"uid":365620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T04:20:54.000Z","msg":"早年提倡漢字簡化的人蓄意以「繁體字」指稱自古傳承下來的正體字，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">目的是要強調正體字的筆畫繁多難以學習</span></span>，藉以突顯簡體字的優點。<br />\n<br />\n記得之前馬英九要求將繁體字正名為正體字，中共又係表示<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">強烈反對</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔係想話咩中國撚一定要傳承中華文化之類嘅大中華膠思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而係「繁體字」呢個名，的確係令人聯想到<strong>「繁複、繁瑣」</strong>嘅概念，呢樣亦係中共最擅長嘅<span class=\"large\"><strong><strong><strong><span class=\"red\">偷換概念</span></strong></strong></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老老豆豆，我覺得呢個偷換概念對我哋成年人/呢一代嘅人無咩大影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但對於小朋友/下一代嘅人呢？<br />\n<br />\n加上支那一直想消滅香港本土文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「繁體字」呢個名喺潛移默化下，會唔會令小朋友對正體字有負面印象？<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">重點</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我哋要畀下一代知道，正體字唔係咩繁瑣嘅字體<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"gold\">正體字係優越過殘體字<br />\n殘體字係畀文盲用嘅字</span><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">要矮化返殘體字，令小朋友為自己使用正體字而自豪</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要防止被文化入侵，首先要為自己嘅文化自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cde1f41cf0cf7fd0ed45e646721798b31de7226","tid":2209916,"uid":283741,"like":0,"dislike":36,"score":-36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T04:29:49.000Z","msg":"叫煩體字最貼切。<br />\n你解釋到點解唔寫匚丯，要寫多幾十筆嘅匯豐先講啦。<br />\n煩體好殘體好，一種落後嘅下流語言本身就應該消失，唔需要再拗邊種字體好，根本所有都係垃圾"},{"pid":"432c8c3d190dc30313fa306c280f9534a33452f9","tid":2209916,"uid":102997,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8cde1f41cf0cf7fd0ed45e646721798b31de7226","tid":2209916,"uid":283741,"like":0,"dislike":36,"score":-36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T04:29:49.000Z","msg":"叫煩體字最貼切。<br />\n你解釋到點解唔寫匚丯，要寫多幾十筆嘅匯豐先講啦。<br />\n煩體好殘體好，一種落後嘅下流語言本身就應該消失，唔需要再拗邊種字體好，根本所有都係垃圾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T04:31:37.000Z","msg":"因為柒囉<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368a9998b6f12b54c9da8697ae0c9e8e37a6ba50","tid":2209916,"uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T04:33:54.000Z","msg":"ok以後叫正體字"},{"pid":"edeb25a6e89c373ae95d40ac24b265afe4fbd047","tid":2209916,"uid":78392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T04:34:19.000Z","msg":"不嬲都叫支那個隻係文盲體<br />\n因為係俾文盲既人睇<br />\n好似武漢肺炎係武漢爆出黎<br />\n就叫武漢肺炎"},{"pid":"981a81c5e5485d512fff22958f618b5e8c5483a6","tid":2209916,"uid":152944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T04:37:42.000Z","msg":"唔係不嬲都叫正體中文咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4e6d7f011173380485da984e01d3002e6f9caa","tid":2209916,"uid":365620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"981a81c5e5485d512fff22958f618b5e8c5483a6","tid":2209916,"uid":152944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T04:37:42.000Z","msg":"唔係不嬲都叫正體中文咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T04:39:03.000Z","msg":"好多人都仲叫緊繁體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\neven連登仔"},{"pid":"c1dcbbf51f1de3323ba945578e0717e9f2f2d1c7","tid":2209916,"uid":283741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"432c8c3d190dc30313fa306c280f9534a33452f9","tid":2209916,"uid":102997,"like":3,"dislike":0,"sco